MAVEN INSTALLIATION PROCESS
**************************************
Step 1:In vm go to the /opt directory and install the java-21-openjdk-devel git wget tar unzip 

Step 2:Go to the browser search 'apache maven download' enter the maven download copy the 'apache-maven-3.9.14-bin.tar.gz' this link address

Step 3:in vm paste the link address
  example : wget https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.9.14/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.14-bin.tar.gz

Step 4:then install maven and create one maven file

Step 5:Here maven and crated one file then extract the maven file
    example : tar -xvf apache-maven-3.9.14-bin.tar.gz
>after extract the file crate a one directory

Step 5:Rename that directory by using mv command
  
   command & example : mv apache-maven-3.9.14 maven

Step 6:create a java & git path
     command :which java ----> /usr/bin/java
              which git -----> /usr/bin/git
>enter the /usr/lib/jvm copy this : /usr/lib/jvm/java-21-openjdk-21.0.10.0.7-1.el9.x86_64

Step 7:create the path 
  
  export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-21-openjdk-21.0.10.0.7-1.el9.x86_64
export PATH=$PATH:/usr/lib/jvm/java-21-openjdk-21.0.10.0.7-1.el9.x86_64/bin

export M2_HOME=/opt/maven
export PATH=$PATH:/opt/maven/bin

export PATH=$PATH:/usr/bin/git

Step 8:Goto the ~/.bashrc file
     
     command :vim ~/.bashrc
     copy the path in this file

     command :source ~/bashrc
    This command use reload the file and apply the changes
    
Step 9:Now maven is created apply the command
  
   command :mvn --version
   




